      "author": "s-blu",
      "description": "## Core functionality release\r\n- Saves scrolls of all open editors when using mouse wheel or scroll bar \r\n- Provides ribbon icon & command to manually restore scroll position if wished (configurable in settings)\r\n- Provides maximum age of scroll positions to apply\r\n\r\n\r\n## Limitations\r\n\r\n- Does not restore nor save scroll positions for notes in Read Mode\r\n- Does not save scroll positions when using the mouse wheel and switching the tab while scrolling\r\n- No visual indicator of the saved scroll position yet",
